Day 3 - Chapter 2
2) Modulo Operator
The modulo operator % gives you the remainder after division.

Example:- 
i)
print(10 % 3)  # 1  
print(8 % 2)   # 0  
print(7 % 4)   # 3  

ii)
number_to_check = int(input("What is yo number?!"))
if number_to_check % 2 == 0:
  print("Even")
else:
  print("Odd")
